      "content": "that seems pretty one-sided though. isn't there an argument that the UN actually helps prevent bigger conflicts by providing a space for diplomacy, even if they can't stop every single war? like, wouldn't some historians say the problem isn't the UN itself, but just how hard it is to get every country to agree on anything?",
